## 🔧 调试工具箱

### 日志工具

**Python**:
```python
# 标准日志
import logging
logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)

# 结构化日志
import structlog
logger = structlog.get_logger()

# 日志配置
logging.basicConfig(
    level=logging.INFO,
    format='%(asctime)s - %(name)s - %(levelname)s - %(message)s'
)
```

**JavaScript**:
```javascript
// 标准日志
console.log('Info')
console.error('Error')
console.warn('Warning')

// 结构化日志
import winston from 'winston'
const logger = winston.createLogger({
  format: winston.format.json(),
  transports: [new winston.transports.File({ filename: 'app.log' })]
})
```

### 调试器

**Python**:
```python
# pdb 调试
import pdb; pdb.set_trace()

# ipdb (增强版)
import ipdb; ipdb.set_trace()

# VS Code 调试
# 设置断点，使用调试面板
```

**JavaScript**:
```javascript
// Chrome DevTools
debugger;

// Node.js Inspector
node --inspect app.js
```

### 性能分析

**Python**:
```bash
# cProfile
python -m cProfile app.py

# py-spy
py-spy record -- python app.py

# memory_profiler
@mprof.profile
def my_function():
    ...
```

**JavaScript**:
```bash
# Chrome Profiler
# 打开 DevTools → Performance

# clinic.js
clinic doctor -- node app.js
```

### 网络工具

```bash
# API 测试
curl -X GET http://api.example.com/users
http GET http://api.example.com/users

# 网络抓包
wireshark
tcpdump -i eth0 port 80

# 性能测试
ab -n 1000 -c 10 http://api.example.com/
```

